Go to internet browser.

Download files from galaxy to documents folder.

Return to terminal

In Terminal, type gedit problem3

Copy & paste this script:
 
 #!/bin/bash
 for file in ~/Downloads
            if [ sequence > 40bp]; then
               echo expression evaluated as true
            else
               run 
            fi
           
Save file and close.
In terminal, type: chmod 755 problem3
then: bash problem3

in the terminal, type: trim_galore -q 30 --length 18 --fastqc phiXs_8_1_sequence.100k.fastq
